tle> Re: Mythic and nerfs - long</span><hr size=1> me not good at long writings (I'm only a tank after all <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>About nerfs, all I have to say is: I never liked it when someone changed the rules in the middle of the game.<br><br>Well I'm quiting the game today, not that I don't like the game, it's just my summer break <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I've got so many flowers needing my attention, outdoor BBQs, evenings at the lake aroud the camp fire... summer is too short here, no time for computer games!<br><br>See you all in fall, where ever you are then.<br><br>Have Fun!<br>Dia<br><br>  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/umonnkee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>monnkee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/15/02 8:31:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1130.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mythic and nerfs - long</span><hr size=1> The bottem line is this no game can predict human AI no matter how well they THINK they have classes balanced along comes someone with a new tactic that they didnt count on and they are back to the drawing board again.  No matter what changes mythic makes good or bad someone is gonna be unhappy, no one can please everyone no matter what game all you can do is adapt to the changes they have made and there WILL be changes no online game can survive without them there is a reason that stealthers are usually the top RP earners on almost all the servers whether they be archers or 